snippet.title: Mata Nui Online Game 2 Walkthrough Part 1: Ga-Koro
snippet.description:
Be kind to your eyes. Watch in HD.
Welcome again, weary traveler. Take my hand and let us now travel back to the time that many considered to have been Bionicle's height. Take my hand and let us journey back to 2003, the days of the Toa Nuva, Bohrok-Kal, Rahkshi, and the quest for the Toa of Light. Take my hand and let us travel back to "Bionicle: Mata Nui Online Game 2".

Highlights of this video include: 
-meeting Amaya
-collecting cowrie shells and seaweed
-fixing hole in roof
-making flax
-fixing bridge
-creating a kohli stick

Link to this game: (requires account on biomediaproject)
http://biomediaproject.com/bmp/files/gms/online/hahli/
